Manning STREWL, Appellant, v. W. H. HIATT, Warden, United States Penitentiary, Atlanta, Ga., Appellee. No. 12558 United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. May 3, 1949. Manning Strewl, of Atlanta, Ga., in pro. per. J. Ellis Mundy, U. S. Atty., and Harvey H. Tisinger, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of Atlanta, Ga., for appellee.

Before HOLMES, McCORD, and WALLER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the lower Court is affirmed.
